7.Write a shell script to print all files name and size greater than 5K

Ans=> for i in *
	do
		if [ -e $i ]
		then
			file=`ls -l $i | awk '{print $5}'`
			if (( $file > 5000 ))
			then
				ls -l $i
			fi 
		fi
	done














