1. Write a script To check given year is leap or not.
Ans=> echo "Enter an Year"
	  read yr
	  if [ $yr%4 -eq 0 ] && [ $yr%100 -eq 0 ] && [ $yr%400 -eq 0 ]
	  then
			echo "It is leap year"
	  else
			echo "It is not leap year"
			
