2. Write a script to print day of the week using
	a) elif	b) case 
	Ans=> echo "Enter the no. of the Day "
	read day

	if [ $day == 1 ]
	then
		echo "Sunday"
	elif [ $day == 2 ]
	then
		echo "Monday"
	elif [ $day == 3 ]
	then
		echo "Tuesday"
	elif [ $day == 4 ]
	then
		echo "Wednesday"
	elif [ $day == 5 ]
	then
		echo "Thrusday"
	elif [ $day == 6 ]
	then
		echo "Friday"
	elif [ $day == 7 ]
	then
		echo "Saturday"
	else
		echo "Invalid"
	fi

